headline.main: Bjoergen Grabs Gold as Norway Sweep Medals in Women's 30km
headline.print_headline: Bjoergen Grabs Gold as Norway Sweep Medals in Women's 30km

lead_paragraph: Marit Bjoergen secured yet another gold medal at the Nordic World Ski Championships as her Norwegian team stormed home to take the top four positions in the women's 30km mass start on Saturday.
